entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="mex" o="Ey, ¿has visto a Chuckie? ¿Dónde andará metido?" t="Ey, you seen Chuckie? Where's he been?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="mex" o="¡¿Qué?! ¡¿Cómo?!" t="What?! How?!" b="" a=""/>
Ehh... He found a Kiroshi. New model, barely used, a real find. Told 'im to sell it... but no. Gonk had to have those peepers for himself.
Anyways, we was just walkin'... Suddenly this black van zooms over. They brain me, Chuck gets a bag over his head, in he goes.
Million eds say it was those optics. You know how it goes – cut 'em outta him, tossed the meat.
